cs.AI, cs.LO, cs.DS, cs.GT, cs.PL. 

The paper deals with a constraint-based formalism for temporal planning, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of Mean Payoff Games and the connection with Hyper Temporal Networks suggests a focus on algorithms and data structures (cs.DS) and graph theory (cs.GT). The paper also involves formal verification and logic (cs.LO) and constraint programming (cs.PL).
